metadata.name: Night Visions 01
metadata.description:
Night Visions 01 is a fine art photography essay in collaboration with Photographer Quinton Cameron of Melinart Productions taken at Thunder Studios in LA.  

*** Open Edition in Commemoration of my first showing at NFT.NYC 2023!**

Night Visions 01 commemorates my first show at NFT.NYC 2023 in the Artist's Village at the Javits Center in NYC showing from April 11-15, 2023.   

Night Visions 01 is a study on how we might see beauty, self expression, and how art makes us feel, particularly 
in the evening hours.  All of my art is designed to provoke feelings of harmony and happiness.  I hope you enjoy this first of many Open Editions in collaboration with photographer Quinton Cameron, better knows as Q!  
Pictured are models Brooke Bates and Natalie Wojtaszek!  
Date of photo:  September 2022
